Title: Sparks Don't Ask
---
Give me this, Lord.
Show me the way.
Reveal to me.
May I share in eternal life.
No, Eckhart!
True obedience makes no requests.
Sparks don't ask
what flames them.
Wanting -- douses them for sure.
